src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/Gamedust_ExtraDesc_Button_Separator__RadekBazak__2021_.PNG?t=1635501043\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/Gamedust_ExtraDesc_Button_IG_RadekBazak.2021.PNG?t=1635501043\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/Gamedust_ExtraDesc_Separator__RadekBazak__2021_.PNG?t=1635501043\" /></span><br><strong>Space music for free!</strong><br><br>We know a lot of people love Yupitergrad’s music - that's why the full soundtrack of the game is available on Steam. However, many players do not play in VR yet, and we want to prepare something for them too - so that they can <strong>feel the cosmos in their ears and hearts</strong>...<br><br>This is why <strong>Yupitergrad: Sneaki Soundtrack</strong> was created. It is a collection of new songs that appeared in the game along with updates.<br>You can <strong>download them for free</strong> and check if you feel like part of the universe.  😄<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE GAME</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/5ae586f485dfd84a865ad78b1fcebdb1.poster.avif?t=1635501043\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/5ae586f485dfd84a865ad78b1fcebdb1.webm?t=1635501043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/5ae586f485dfd84a865ad78b1fcebdb1.mp4?t=1635501043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🌟🌌 ＦＥＡＴＵＲＥＳ 🌌🌟</strong><br>🚀 <strong>Minimal risk of motion sickness</strong> thanks to innovative design.<br>🚀 Over <strong>50 tight-packed levels</strong> to explore and conquer.<br>🚀 <strong>Indiana Jones</strong>-like navigation via grappling hooks and boosters.<br>🚀 Lots of crazy <strong>platforming stunts</strong>.<br>🚀 Riddles and <strong>spatial puzzles</strong>.<br>🚀 &quot;<strong>Dieselpunk</strong> in space&quot; atmosphere.<br>🚀 <strong>Time attack mode</strong> where you swing through <strong>40 arcade levels</strong> and compare the score on <strong>leaderboards</strong><br>🚀 <strong>Gymnasion Mode </strong>- a place where you can swing and train crazy stunts;<br>🚀 Slavik humor and peculiar story.<br>🚀 Original, stylized art.<br>🚀 <strong>Soundtrack</strong> by acclaimed video games music composer - <strong>Piotr Surmacz</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/6ba714c2696a4fdbdb4ff95dac6a8a57.poster.avif?t=1635501043\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/6ba714c2696a4fdbdb4ff95dac6a8a57.webm?t=1635501043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/6ba714c2696a4fdbdb4ff95dac6a8a57.mp4?t=1635501043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🌟🌌 ＳＵＭＭＡＲＹ 🌌🌟</strong><br>【Can you imagine VR game almost <strong>free of motion sickness or headaches</strong>? How about <strong>roaming through industrial space station with grappling hooks</strong> and spatial boosters like a <strong>space Indiana Jones</strong>? Ever wanted to see the perspective of a <strong>space comrade</strong>, all soaked in <strong>Dieselpunk</strong> vibe? Or wondered how <strong>acrobatics in space</strong>, zapping off ledges and walls, would feel like?<br><br>【Well look no further <strong>Yupitergrad</strong> is THE complete package - of ALL above. <strong>Arcade platforming</strong>  like you haven't seen before. Spatial riddles where you need to be both <strong>dexterous and quick-thinking</strong>. All bathed in gritty, Slavik, humorous story and wacky acrobatics you simply <strong>WON'T find ANYWHERE</strong> else.<br><br>【So, my dear comrade...<br>...ready to become the <strong>Space Soviet Tarzan™</strong>...? 👨‍🚀<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/3e694e26f679467c1d44ddeeaecdfd67.poster.avif?t=1635501043\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/3e694e26f679467c1d44ddeeaecdfd67.webm?t=1635501043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782140/extras/3e694e26f679467c1d44ddeeaecdfd67.mp4?t=1635501043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
